{{Lunisolar May}} '''May 11''' is the 11th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|de|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|zh|Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|708|de|708|ja|708|zh|708|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 3|de|June 3|ja|June 3|zh|June 3|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Japan’s first domestically produced coin, the silver coin {{ill|Wadō Kaikin|de|和同開珎|ja|和同開珎|zh|和同開珎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, was minted; later in August, a practical copper currency was issued. * {{ill|Tenpyō|de|Tenpyō|ja|天平|zh|Tenpyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 17th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|de|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|zh|Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|745|de|745|ja|745|zh|745|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 15|de|June 15|ja|June 15|zh|June 15|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Emperor {{ill|Shōmu|de|Emperor Shōmu|ja|聖武天皇|zh|Emperor Shōmu|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} restored the capital to {{ill|Heijō-kyō|de|Heijō-kyō|ja|平城京|zh|Heijō-kyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Juei|de|Juei|ja|寿永|zh|Juei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|de|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|zh|Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1183|de|1183|ja|1183|zh|1183|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 2|de|June 2|ja|June 2|zh|June 2|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Battle of Tsurinawa Mountain ({{ill|Tsurinawa no Tatakai|ja|倶利伽羅峠の戦い|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) took place, with {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|de|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|ja|源義仲|zh|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} defeating {{ill|Taira no Yoshiakira|de|Taira no Yoshiakira|ja|平維盛|zh|平維盛|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Bun'ei|de|Bun'ei|ja|文永|zh|Bun'ei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|de|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|zh|Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1274|de|1274|ja|1274|zh|1274|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 16|de|June 16|ja|June 16|zh|June 16|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Exiled