raft}}) – Exiled monk {{ill|Nichiren|de|Nichiren|ja|日蓮|zh|Nichiren|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was pardoned by the bakufu and left Kamakura for 【Minobu-san|身延山】. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1576|de|1576|ja|1576|zh|1576|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 7|de|June 7|ja|June 7|zh|June 7|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Tenshu (main tower) of {{ill|Azuchi Castle|de|安土城|ja|安土城|zh|安土城|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was completed; shortly thereafter, {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|de|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|zh|Oda Nobunaga|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} relocated from {{ill|Gifu Castle|de|岐阜城|ja|岐阜城|zh|岐阜城|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. == Births ==
