== Events == * {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|708|de|708|ja|708|zh|708|qq=}} {{ill|June 3|de|June 3|ja|June 3|zh|June 3|qq=}}) – Japan’s first domestically produced coin, the silver coin {{ill|Wadō Kaikin|de|和同開珎|ja|和同開珎|zh|和同開珎|qq=}}, was minted; later in August, a practical copper currency was issued. * {{ill|Tenpyō|de|Tenpyō|ja|天平|zh|Tenpyō|qq=}} 17th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|745|de|745|ja|745|zh|745|qq=}} {{ill|June 15|de|June 15|ja|June 15|zh|June 15|qq=}}) – Emperor {{ill|Shōmu|de|Emperor Shōmu|ja|聖武天皇|zh|Emperor Shōmu|qq=}} restored the capital to {{ill|Heijō-kyō|de|Heijō-kyō|ja|平城京|zh|Heijō-kyō|qq=}}. * {{ill|Juei|de|Juei|ja|寿永|zh|Juei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1183|de|1183|ja|1183|zh|1183|qq=}} {{ill|June 2|de|June 2|ja|June 2|zh|June 2|qq=}}) – The Battle of Tsurinawa Mountain ({{ill|Tsurinawa no Tatakai|ja|倶利伽羅峠の戦い|qq=}}) took place, with {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|de|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|ja|源義仲|zh|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|qq=}} defeating {{ill|Taira no Yoshiakira|de|Taira no Yoshiakira|ja|平維盛|zh|平維盛|qq=}}. * {{ill|Bun'ei|de|Bun'ei|ja|文永|zh|Bun'ei|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1274|de|1274|ja|1274|zh|1274|qq=}} {{ill|June 16|de|June 16|ja|June 16|zh|June 16|qq=}}) – Exiled monk {{ill|Nichiren|de|Nichiren|ja|日蓮|zh|Nichiren|qq=}} was pardoned by the bakufu and left Kamakura for 【Minobu-san|身延山】. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1576|de|1576|ja|1576|zh|1576|qq=}} {{ill|June 7|de|June 7|ja|June 7|zh|June 7|qq=}}) – The Tenshu (main tower) of {{ill|Azuchi Castle|de|安土城|ja|安土城|zh|安土城|qq=}} was completed; shortly thereafter, {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|de|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|zh|Oda Nobunaga|qq=}} relocated from {{ill|Gifu Castle|de|岐阜城|ja|岐阜城|zh|岐阜城|qq=}}. == Births ==
== Deaths == * {{ill|Bunmei|ja|文明|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1473|de|1473|ja|1473|zh|1473|qq=}} {{ill|June 6|de|June 6|ja|June 6|zh|June 6|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hosokawa Katsumoto|de|細川勝元|ja|細川勝元|zh|細川勝元|qq=}}, a military commander (born {{ill|1430|de|1430|ja|1430|zh|1430|qq=}}). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=}} 1st year (leap May) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=}} {{ill|1865|de|1865|ja|1865|zh|1865|qq=}} {{ill|July 3|de|July 3|ja|July 3|zh|July 3|qq=}}) – {{ill|Okada Izō|de|岡田以蔵|ja|岡田以蔵|zh|岡田以蔵|qq=}}, a Sonnō jōi faction activist (born {{ill|1838|de|1838|ja|1838|zh|1838|qq=}}). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=}} 1st year (leap May) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=}} {{ill|1865|de|1865|ja|1865|zh|1865|qq=}} {{ill|July 3|de|July 3|ja|July 3|zh|July 3|qq=}}) – {{ill|Takechi Zuizan|de|武市瑞山|ja|武市瑞山|zh|武市瑞山|qq=}}, also known as Takechi Hanpeita, another Sonnō jōi faction activist (born {{ill|1829|de|1829|ja|1829|zh|1829|qq=}}). * {{ill|Meiji era|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|lt=Meiji|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=}} {{ill|1869|de|1869|ja|1869|zh|1869|qq=}} {{ill|June 20|de|June 20|ja|June 20|zh|June 20|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hijikata Toshizō|de|土方歳三|ja|土方歳三|zh|土方歳三|qq=}}, the vice-commander of the {{ill|Shinsengumi|de|新選組|ja|新選組|zh|新選組|qq=}} (born {{ill|1835|de|1835|ja|1835|zh|1835|qq=}}).
