* {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year (leap May) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1865|de|1865|ja|1865|zh|1865|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|July 3|de|July 3|ja|July 3|zh|July 3|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Takechi Zuizan|de|武市瑞山|ja|武市瑞山|zh|武市瑞山|qq=|12=draft}}, also known as Takechi Hanpeita, another Sonnō jōi faction activist (born {{ill|1829|de|1829|ja|1829|zh|1829|qq=|12=draft}}).
