{{Lunisolar May|qq=}}
'''May 11''' is the 11th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Wadō|ja|和銅|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|708|de|708|ja|708|zh|708|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 3|de|June 3|ja|June 3|zh|June 3|qq=|12=draft}}) – Japan’s first domestically produced coin, the silver coin {{ill|Wadō Kaikin|de|和同開珎|ja|和同開珎|zh|和同開珎|qq=|12=draft}}, was minted; later in August, a practical copper currency was issued.
* {{ill|Tenpyō|de|Tenpyō|ja|天平|zh|Tenpyō|qq=|12=draft}} 17th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|745|de|745|ja|745|zh|745|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 15|de|June 15|ja|June 15|zh|June 15|qq=|12=draft}}) – Emperor {{ill|Shōmu|de|Emperor Shōmu|ja|聖武天皇|zh|Emperor Shōmu|qq=|12=draft}} restored the capital to {{ill|Heijō-kyō|de|Heijō-kyō|ja|平城京|zh|Heijō-kyō|qq=|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Juei|de|Juei|ja|寿永|zh|Juei|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1183|de|1183|ja|1183|zh|1183|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 2|de|June 2|ja|June 2|zh|June 2|qq=|12=draft}}) – The Battle of Tsurinawa Mountain ({{ill|Tsurinawa no Tatakai|ja|倶利伽羅峠の戦い|qq=|12=draft}}) took place, with {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|de|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|ja|源義仲|zh|Minamoto no Yoshinaka|qq=|12=draft}} defeating {{ill|Taira no Yoshiakira|de|Taira no Yoshiakira|ja|平維盛|zh|平維盛|qq=|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Bun'ei|de|Bun'ei|ja|文永|zh|Bun'ei|qq=|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1274|de|1274|ja|1274|zh|1274|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 16|de|June 16|ja|June 16|zh|June 16|qq=|12=draft}}) – Exiled monk {{ill|Nichiren|de|Nichiren|ja|日蓮|zh|Nichiren|qq=|12=draft}} was pardoned by the bakufu and left Kamakura for 【Minobu-san|身延山】.
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1576|de|1576|ja|1576|zh|1576|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|June 7|de|June 7|ja|June 7|zh|June 7|qq=|12=draft}}) – The Tenshu (main tower) of {{ill|Azuchi Castle|de|安土城|ja|安土城|zh|安土城|qq=|12=draft}} was completed; shortly thereafter, {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|de|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|zh|Oda Nobunaga|qq=|12=draft}} relocated from {{ill|Gifu Castle|de|岐阜城|ja|岐阜城|zh|岐阜城|qq=|12=draft}}.
