горианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1865|de|1865|ja|1865|zh|1865|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|July 3|de|July 3|ja|July 3|zh|July 3|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Takechi Zuizan|de|武市瑞山|ja|武市瑞山|zh|武市瑞山|qq=|qq=draft}}, also known as Takechi Hanpeita, another Sonnō jōi faction activist (born {{ill|1829|de|1829|ja|1829|zh|1829|qq=|qq=draft}}). * {{ill|Meiji era|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|lt=Meiji|qq=|qq=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1869|de|1869|ja|1869|zh|1869|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|June 20|de|June 20|ja|June 20|zh|June 20|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Hijikata Toshizō|de|土方歳三|ja|土方歳三|zh|土方歳三|qq=|qq=draft}}, the vice-commander of the {{ill|Shinsengumi|de|新選組|ja|新選組|zh|新選組|qq=|qq=draft}} (born {{ill|1835|de|1835|ja|1835|zh|1835|qq=|qq=draft}}).
