== Events == * [[:en:Wadō (era)|Wadō]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|708|de|708|ja|708|zh|708|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/708|qq=}} {{ill|June 3|de|June 3|ja|June 3|zh|June 3|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 3|qq=}}) – Japan’s first domestically produced coin, the silver coin [[:en:Wadōkaichin|Wadō Kaikin]], was minted; later in August, a practical copper currency was issued. * [[:en:Tenpyō|Tenpyō]] 17th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|745|de|745|ja|745|zh|745|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/745|qq=}} {{ill|June 15|de|June 15|ja|June 15|zh|June 15|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 15|qq=}}) – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Shōmu|Shōmu]] restored the capital to [[:en:Heijō-kyō|Heijō-kyō]]. * [[:en:Juei|Juei]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1183|de|1183|ja|1183|zh|1183|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1183|qq=}} {{ill|June 2|de|June 2|ja|June 2|zh|June 2|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 2|qq=}}) – The Battle of Tsurinawa Mountain ([[:en:Battle of Kurikara Pass|Tsurinawa no Tatakai]]) took place, with [[:en:Minamoto no Yoshinaka|Minamoto no Yoshinaka]] defeating [[:en:Taira no Koremori|Taira no Yoshiakira]]. * [[:en:Bun'ei|Bun'ei]] 11th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1274|de|1274|ja|1274|zh|1274|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1274|qq=}} {{ill|June 16|de|June 16|ja|June 16|zh|June 16|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 16|qq=}}) – Exiled monk [[:en:Nichiren|Nichiren]] was pardoned by the bakufu and left Kamakura for 【Minobu-san|身延山】. * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 4th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1576|de|1576|ja|1576|zh|1576|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1576|qq=}} {{ill|June 7|de|June 7|ja|June 7|zh|June 7|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 7|qq=}}) – The Tenshu (main tower) of [[:en:Azuchi Castle|Azuchi Castle]] was completed; shortly thereafter, [[:en:Oda Nobunaga|Oda Nobunaga]] relocated from [[:en:Gifu Castle|Gifu Castle]]. == Births ==
== Deaths == * [[:en:Civilization|Bunmei]] 5th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1473|de|1473|ja|1473|zh|1473|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1473|qq=}} {{ill|June 6|de|June 6|ja|June 6|zh|June 6|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 6|qq=}}) – [[:en:Hosokawa Katsumoto|Hosokawa Katsumoto]], a military commander (born {{ill|1430|de|1430|ja|1430|zh|1430|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1430|qq=}}). * [[:en:Keiō|Keiō]] 1st year (leap May) ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1865|de|1865|ja|1865|zh|1865|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1865|qq=}} {{ill|July 3|de|July 3|ja|July 3|zh|July 3|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 3|qq=}}) – [[:en:Okada Izō|Okada Izō]], a Sonnō jōi faction activist (born {{ill|1838|de|1838|ja|1838|zh|1838|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1838|qq=}}). * [[:en:Keiō|Keiō]] 1st year (leap May) ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1865|de|1865|ja|1865|zh|1865|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1865|qq=}} {{ill|July 3|de|July 3|ja|July 3|zh|July 3|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 3|qq=}}) – [[:en:Takechi Hanpeita|Takechi Zuizan]], also known as Takechi Hanpeita, another Sonnō jōi faction activist (born {{ill|1829|de|1829|ja|1829|zh|1829|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1829|qq=}}). * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1869|de|1869|ja|1869|zh|1869|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1869|qq=}} {{ill|June 20|de|June 20|ja|June 20|zh|June 20|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 20|qq=}}) – [[:en:Hijikata Toshizō|Hijikata Toshizō]], the vice-commander of the [[:en:Shinsengumi|Shinsengumi]] (born {{ill|1835|de|1835|ja|1835|zh|1835|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1835|qq=}}).
